Package: keramik
Version: 0.20020529
Revision: 2
Depends: kdelibs3 (>= 3.0.1-1) | kdelibs3-ssl (>= 3.0.1-1), kdebase3 (>= 3.0.1-1) | kdebase3-ssl (>= 3.0.1-1), dlcompat, libpng-shlibs, qt3-shlibs
BuildDepends: kdelibs3-dev (>= 3.0.1-1) | kdelibs3-ssl-dev (>= 3.0.1-1), kdebase3-dev (>= 3.0.1-1) | kdebase3-ssl-dev (>= 3.0.1-1), fink (>= 0.9.12), automake15, autoconf25, libtool14, dlcompat, libpng, qt3
Maintainer: Benjamin Reed <ranger@befunk.com>
Source: http://apps.kde.com/na/2/counter/vid/7337/dld0/%n-05292002.tar.bz2
SourceDirectory: %n
PatchScript: sed 's|@PREFIX@|%p|g' <%a/%f.patch | patch -p1
SetLDFLAGS: -L%p/lib
SetCPPFLAGS: -no-cpp-precomp
SetCFLAGS: -fno-common
ConfigureParams: --prefix=%p --with-qt-dir=%p --with-extra-libs=%p/lib --with-extra-includes=%p/include --enable-mt --with-pic --enable-rpath --enable-shared=yes --mandir=%i/share/man --with-xinerama --enable-final $KDEOPTS
CompileScript: <<
 make -f Makefile.cvs
 (export KDEDIR=%p; sh configure %c; make)
<<
InstallScript: <<
 make install DESTDIR=%d
 rm -rf %i/bin
 rm -rf %i/include
 rm -rf %i/lib/kwin.*
 rm -rf %i/lib/libkdefx*
 rm -rf %i/share
<<
Description: The Keramik style and window theme for KDE.
DescDetail: <<
This release was packaged together by Codre Adrian using the Keramik style
from kdelibs CVS and the Keramik decorations from kdebase CVS and
adjusting the build environment.
<<
DescPort: <<
NOTE: KDE packages do *not* have an -shlibs because of KDE's use of  
libltdl!  The .la's *must* be used in conjunction with the dynamic
libraries, and they are unversioned filenames, so multiple -shlibs would
conflict.
<<
